product.name: Foho Vacuum Stand Compatible for Dyson V15 V11 V10 V8 V7 V6, Metal Storage Bracket Stand Holder Compatible for Dyson Handheld DC30 DC31 DC34 DC35 DC58 DC59 DC62 Cordless Vacuum Cleaners & Accessories
product.bullet_points:
• 【Compatible Models】Specially Designed for Dyson V11 V10 V8 V7 V6 DC30 DC31 DC34 DC35 DC58 DC59 DC62 DC74 Handheld Cordless Vacuum Cleaner.【Notice】The vacuum cleaner and accessories shown on the photos are for visual demonstration purposes ONLY
• 【Sturdy and Stable Design】Heavy base(11.5*8.7 in, 6 lb), with 4 long screws connecting metal frame at the bottom for security. Made of metal curved flat iron, with a 50” height steel tower structure. These design prevent the bracket stand from swinging
• 【No Drilling In the Wall】Premium floor docking stand for cordless vacuum cleaners. No more worry about drilling holes in your wall for the docking station! Our premium quality freestanding floor stand is perfect for storing your cordless vacuum cleaner
• 【Saving Space and Time】Get all the accessories in the metal holders. Easily organize the mess of your attachments, save your house space. No longer forget where is your next Dyson cleaner head when you use them, save much time to clean your house
• 【Easy to Assemble】A sufficient number of high quality stainless steel parts and simple installation instructions make it easy to assemble this bracket, which is suitable for corners and crevices and will help you save more space
